MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-179. Jenkins v. Parkview Counseling Ctr., Inc.

Mahoning County, No. 92 C.A. 42. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of *1418Appeals for Mahoning County to certify its record. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective February 16, 1993.
